userdoc.notice: The purpose of this contract is to hold BUSDC tokens for gas compensation: https://github.com/liquity/dev#gas-compensation When a borrower opens a trove, an additional 50 BUSDC debt is issued, and 50 BUSDC is minted and sent to this contract. When a borrower closes their active trove, this gas compensation is refunded: 50 BUSDC is burned from the this contract's balance, and the corresponding 50 BUSDC debt on the trove is cancelled. See this issue for more context: https://github.com/liquity/dev/issues/186
